"gg_rmdeath2"

This is a small sized symmetrical GG map. This is the second version of the first map I made for CS:S.  I left the layout the same but I've reworked the textures, rebalanced the layout slightly, and added more details.
Buy Zones are included for Fight Yard style play too.

Please download, comment and enjoy!

- 48 Spawns
- Cubemaps
- Optimized for better FPS
- Overview radar map
- Buy Zones
- Nav File
- Pakrat
